data.title: Archana (actress)
data.text:
Archana (born as Sudha) is an Indian film actress and Kuchipudi and Kathak dancer, known for her works in Tollywood, Kollywood and Malayalam cinema. She is the recipient of two National Film Awards.[1][2]In November 2020, she appeared in the longest running Telugu Television Talk show Alitho Saradaga in Episode 201 hosted by Tollywood actor-comedian Ali.[3]

For other actresses named Archana, see Archana (disambiguation).
